---

<Layout name="tropical's site" title="tropical's site" description="hi there">
	<main>
		<aside>
			<section class="top">
				<h1>Tropical</h1>
				<span>I poke at computers for fun.</span>
			</section>
			<section class="bottom">
				<p>
					Hey, I'm Tropical - a programmer with interests in UI/UX
					design/accessibility, embedded stuff, frontend webdev,
					reverse-engineering, competitive robotics, and music.
					<br />
					<br />
					I've done webdev for ~6 years, but more recently have gotten into embedded. I'm studying CS at <a href="https://auburn.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Auburn</a>.
				</p>

				<div class="buttons">
					<a
						title="GitHub Profile"
						href="https://github.com/tropix126/"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noreferrer noopener"
						style="--animation-stagger-delay: 0ms"
					>
						<svg
							aria-hidden="true"
							xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
							width="24"
							height="24"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-width="2"
							stroke-linecap="round"
